==Korean==
===Noun===
'''볼기''' (''bolgi'') 
#[[buttock]], [[cheek]] cf. German '''[[Backe]]''' (''the bulge of the face and the hip'') 

====Synonyms====
*[[엉덩이]] (''eongdeongI'') [[buttock]], [[hip]] (''upper part'')
*[[궁둥이]]  (''gungdungI'') [[bottom]], [[hip]] (''lower part'')

====Derived terms====
*볼기[[짝]] (''-jjag, -jjak'') (''humble, suggestive of a pair of'') [[buttock]]s

====Related terms====
*[[뺨]] (''ppyam'') [[cheek]]; [[ball]] (''of shoes, feet, toes, thumbs, etc.'') cf. German '''[[Backe]], [[Wange]]'''
*[[볼]] (''bol, bor'') [[cheek]]; [[ball]] (''of shoes, feet, toes, thumbs, etc.'')
*[[불]](''bul'') [[ball]], [[bollock]], [[testicle]]; [[scrotum]]; [[genital]]
*불[[알]] (''bur-al'') [[ball]], [[bollock]], [[testicle]]  
*불[[두덩]] (''bul-dudeong'') [[pubis]] (''of males and females'')
*[[볼록]] (''bollog, bollok'') [[protrusion]], [[convex]]
*[[불룩]] (''bullug, bulluk'') [[protrusion]], [[convex]]
*[[불리다]] (''bullida'') To [[fill]], [[inflate]], [[increase]], [[breed]], [[soak]], [[harden]], to be [[blown]], [[call]]ed
*[[불다]] (''bulda'') To [[blow]]

